Open Community License - Micro Business (Micro v1)

Micro serves solely as an add-on condition for OCL distribution and is effective
only if specifically referenced in said OCL distribution (`OCL v* + Micro v1` or
`Open Community License v* + Micro Business v1`). Such add-on only adds further
binding license condition without any change or invalidation of any part of OCL.

As a commercial BUSINESS USER

YOU MUST NOT use the product and/or its components and/or its derivatives in any
way if your annual gross revenue for the last twelve months exceeds the value of
one-million EURO without obtaining a separate business license.

The revenue includes licensee as well as any affiliates that, directly or
indirectly, control licensee or are controlled by licensee or are under common
control with licensee.
